casebody.data:
DuDONIS v. DIRECTOR OF PATUXENT INSTITUTION [App. No. 54,

September Term, 1964.]

Decided November 13, 1964.

Before Henderson, C. J., and Hammond, Prescott, Horney and Sybert, J'J.

Per Curiam.

Application for leave to appeal from a denial of post conviction relief is denied for the reasons set out in the opinion of Judge Carter in the court below.

Application denied.
